name: OBSERV
description: The mission with OBSERV is to increase awareness about the threats we face with our environment and to encourage individuals to problem solve and participate in the resolution if environmental challenges. We believe the first step a cleaner planet is expanding education in Environmental Education.To help with this issue, our merchandise store (coming soon) will only accept OBSERV tokens as payment. Any profits from the sale of merchandise will go directly to Earthjustice.
